\begin_layout Subsection
回归直线
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
回归直线方程是根据样本资料通过回归分析所得到的反映一个变量（因变量）对另一个或一组变量（自变量）的回归关系的数学表达式。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果散点图中点的分布从整体看大致在一条直线附近，我们就称这两个变量之间具有线性相关关系，这条直线叫做回归直线(
\begin_inset Formula $y=bx+a$
\end_inset

)。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
求回归直线与
\series bold
最小二乘法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
根据统计得到两个具有线性相关关系的变量的一组数据:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(x_{1},y_{1}),(x_{2},y_{2}),\cdots,(x_{n},y_{n})
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
找出直线
\begin_inset Formula $y=bx+a$
\end_inset

与点的距离.
 由于最短距离计算较为复杂, 我们可以用点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{i},y_{i})$
\end_inset

与这条直线上横坐标为的点
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}$
\end_inset

之间的距离来刻画点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{i},y_{i})$
\end_inset

到直线的远近,即用
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
|y_{i}-(bx_{i}+a)|(i=1,2,3,\cdots,n)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
简单一点
\begin_inset Formula $Q=(y_{1}-bx_{1}-a)^{2}+(y_{2}-bx_{2}-a)^{2}+\cdots+(y_{n}-bx_{n}-a)^{2}$
\end_inset

(这个方法也叫
\series bold
最小二乘法
\series default
)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
最后得出所有点整体距离最小
\begin_inset Formula $a,b$
\end_inset

值:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
b=\frac{\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(x_{i}-x)(y_{i}-\overline{y})}{\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(x_{i}-\overline{x})^{2}} & =\frac{\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(x_{i}y_{i}-n\overline{x}\overline{y})}{\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}x_{i}^{2}-n\overline{x}^{2}}\\
a=\overline{y}-b\overline{x}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
回归方程为:
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{y}=bx+a$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中
\begin_inset Formula $x=\frac{1}{n}\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum x_{i}}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $y=\frac{1}{n}\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum y_{i}}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $(x,y)$
\end_inset

 称为
\series bold
样本点的中心
\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果样本点不在回归方程直线上, 可以使用这个模型
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{y}=bx+a+e
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中a,b 位模型的未知参数, e 称为
\series bold
随机误差
\series default
(random error).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
e=
\begin_inset Formula $y-\hat{y}$
\end_inset

,对于样本点而言, 它们的随机误差为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
e_{i}=y_{i}-bx_{i}-a,i=1,2,\cdots,n
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其估值为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{e}_{i}=y_{i}-\hat{y_{i}}=y_{i}-\hat{b}x_{i}-\hat{a},i=1,2,\cdots,n
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{e}$
\end_inset

 称为对应于点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{i},y_{i})$
\end_inset

的
\series bold
残差
\series default
(residual)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
残差图
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
刻画回归线效果:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
R^{2}=1-\frac{\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(y_{i}-\hat{y}_{i})^{2}}{\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(y_{i}-\bar{y}_{i})^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(y_{i}-\bar{y}_{i})^{2}$
\end_inset

是已确定的值, 因此
\begin_inset Formula $R^{2}$
\end_inset

越大, 意味着残差和平方越小
\begin_inset Formula $\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\sum}(y_{i}-\hat{y}_{i})^{2}$
\end_inset

, 即模型效果越好; 
\begin_inset Formula $R^{2}$
\end_inset

 越大反之.
\end_layout

